msgid "A pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power while someone or something rests on top of it."
msgstr ""
"Una piastra a pressione è un componente di pietrarossa che fornisce la "
"corrente di pietrarossa ai blocchi adiacenti mentre qualcuno o qualcosa si "
"trova sopra di essa."

msgid "Provides redstone power when pushed"
msgstr "Fornisce la corrente di pietrarossa quando viene premuto"

msgid "Pushable by players, mobs and objects"
msgstr "Premibile da giocatori, mob ed oggetti"

msgid "Pushable by players and mobs"
msgstr ""

msgid "Pushable by mobs"
msgstr ""

msgid "Pushable by players"
msgstr ""

msgid "Stone Pressure Plate"
msgstr ""

msgid "A stone pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power while a player or mob stands on top of it. It is not triggered by anything else."
msgstr ""

msgid "Polished Blackstone Pressure Plate"
msgstr ""

msgid "A polished blackstone pressure plate is a redstone component which supplies its surrounding blocks with redstone power while a player or mob stands on top of it. It is not triggered by anything else."
msgstr ""
